rComments: Absolutely horrid. Agree, self-righteous, and pretentious. Takes simple material, makes it confusing. Pedagogical talent of a rhesus monkey.

Overrated.  Very disorganized and perhaps the most righteous and pretentious prof at UofT Law.  Seemed way more interested in her personal extra-curricular activities than giving even minimum attention to the lectures.  You've been warned.
A great prof! Very helpful and provides good feedback. Is flexible when it comes to selecting an essay topic.

I took Crim and another immigration course with her.  She sucks- she made mistakes on the Crim exam questions.  I was happy with my marks but would warn you to stay away.  She may be tenured by now.  Too bad. She also figures if you have a Bay St. job she doesn't have to justify her grading.
She's the best, but has high standards
She tries really hard...just a bit unorganized
